{"tid":2518340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李華明：「民主倒退」不只是中央單方面的責任，港人自身也有責任。","createTime":"2021-05-06T03:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T04:42:54.000Z","uid":58612,"like":15,"dislike":279,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"424b21d6a5f1a716fef47507773e1b4f17b5fb90","tid":2518340,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"之前睇完蘋果呢單報道講李華明：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210501/R6H4ZET6ABHLFKFLBUJI7MDFGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210501%2FR6H4ZET6ABHLFKFLBUJI7MDFGE%2F&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=41482cfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210501%2FR6H4ZET6ABHLFKFLBUJI7MDFGE%2F&h=064cbed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210501/R6H4ZET6ABHLFKFLBUJI7MDFGE/</a><br />\n／／涉修改香港選舉制度的法例正在立法會審議，日後參選人須取得選委會5大界別提名，外間關注民主派會否派人參選。民主黨前立法會議員李華明接受建制派傳媒《堅雜誌》訪問時，承認清晰收到中共以不同渠道向民主黨中人發訊息，「表示希望民主黨去選，甚至民主黨誰去選，他們都提出了意見。」李向《蘋果》表示，該黨正就是否參選各自表達意見，會留待9月中委會作最後決定。／／<br />\n<br />\n於是我就走去睇埋堅雜誌原文， 發覺原來佢連抗爭者都屌埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaZe37fSmYpAyFJaj7CTcGZ6jzUzJBXNDJXPRe6NEabdz?filename=eqFDAKG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqFDAKG.png&h=f017ba4e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n// 現時直選議員減至剩20席，他慨嘆是 「民主倒退」 ，對此感到不開心，但他承認這不只是中央單方面的責任，港人自身也有責任。//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6271bebda9c881a5768cc27eceb589da31c58c2","tid":2518340,"uid":152476,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"奶到出汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f8cd767c14d5df5c24457b65fb96ad49a3cc0f","tid":25183